headline: Prediction: 1 Stock That Will Be Worth More Than Verizon 5 Years From Now
summary: Hockey legend Wayne Gretzky once said that part of his greatness was because "I skate to where the puck is going to be, not where it has been."  The ability to anticipate and predict secular trends is also an incredible tool for investors.  Investors have turned to Verizon Wireless (NYSE: VZ) for years, looking for quality returns, and the results haven't been good recently.
